travel.title: Travel
travel.description: Save money on flights and hotels by seeing the world from the comfort of your couch.

592566.title: Over Acadia

0300008995.description: Join travel news journalist Peter Greenberg and his correspondents on exciting global adventures, as he shares tips to improve the travel experience.

01662.title: Europe After Dark
01662.description: EUROPE AFTER DARK is a new TV series based on the Mediterranean island of Ibiza and travels each week to some of the mega dance clubs in one of the ten top European nightlife destinations.

0300005581.title: Under the Pole

0300007262.title: Crossing the Andes
0300007262.description: Why should we keep an eye on Latin America, and which changes are taking place there right now?

0300007591.title: A Long Weekend in... With Rory O’Connell
0300007591.description: The popular Cork chef enjoying the culture as well as the cuisine of eight European cities – Palma de Mallorca, Vienna, Lisbon, Madrid, Bath, Nantes, Copenhagen and Edinburgh.

0300008182.title: Tough Rides: China
0300008182.description: Adventurers Colin and Ryan Pyle embark on an unprecedented motorcycle odyssey, starting in Shanghai and circumnavigating the entire country of China.

0300008850.title: Britain's Hidden Villages
0300008850.description: Join actress Dame Penelope Keith as she visits Britain’s villages to understand the cultural history of these places and their present nature.

0300009014.title: Rustic Adventures: Argentina

0300008647.title: Lidia Celebrates America
0300008647.description: Host Lidia Bastianich gets a taste of the wide array of American culture and food as she meets with families and special celebrity guests.

0300010315.description: In this reality series, homebuyers take a break from city life and bring their island living dreams to life by searching for a place in the Bahamas.

04514.description: Join host Jeff Wilson and PBS award-winning photographers as they ride through a Swiss Alps train adventure. The wonders of the Alps exhilarate travelers as they travel through stunning scenic routes and the great, iconic Matterhorn, a 14,600-foot peak that overlooks the charming town of Zermatt, Switzerland.

0300005900.title: Cities of the World
0300005900.description: Take an incredible journey around the planet to see the most iconic cities known to man. Learn about their histories and vibrant cultures.

0300006026.title: Travel Guides (Australia)

0300007703.description: Join your host Alana Nichols as she hikes through Switzerland's breathtaking countryside and alpine scapes while learning about its history.

0300007547.title: Exotic Destinations 101

It explores the diversity of its landscape from the seas to the arid interior, the effects of flood, drought and bushfire and the impact of over 200 years of European settlement on the land, its plant and animals.

actors: Custodian of the Crown of Romania Margareta
